{"tid":1970181,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「由零開始學，新手學煮飯」— 魚香茄子","createTime":"2020-04-13T03:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T12:05:26.000Z","uid":68594,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"da87d06c3ab748ce1b59660e99d77e361ab26027","tid":1970181,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:07:21.000Z","msg":"大家好！我係子言張！<br />\n我終於試左拍左第一段片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />教大家整魚香茄子。<br />\n<br />\n小弟我真係完全唔識呢啲嘢，有咩改進嘅地方真係要希望大家講聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次菜式入邊會用到料理調味包，因為我覺得唔係個個家庭都會買咁多唔同嘅調味料，尤其是你係一個新手，可能你淨係想煮一次至兩次，所以改用調味包會方便好多，尤其是對完全唔識煮飯嘅新手<br />\n<br />\n成個餸菜由切到煮，到最後調味，都係由我老婆一個新手自己去煮，所以如果發現：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.如果發現切得好危險<br />\n2.落野落得好慢<br />\n3.好似好雞手鴨腳咁樣</span></span><br />\n實屬正常現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5P9dwHo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5P9dwHo.jpg&h=62d8cdb6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7e19bf9c0041ec59f0a0a3545a34259cb558fcf","tid":1970181,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:09:09.000Z","msg":"冇link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8930b13e0b931e5eabe90dda057c2854f604d053","tid":1970181,"uid":74278,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:10:10.000Z","msg":"你會唔會放條片出黎先比較好"},{"pid":"a9c63b8b6b19adcd7075ea5bf9151864b85077d1","tid":1970181,"uid":68594,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:12:30.000Z","msg":"我係智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />影片係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lX3thmvUdvQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlX3thmvUdvQ&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=4c0b95a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lX3thmvUdvQ</a>"},{"pid":"8e5ae039f553e6814b62198297ccbe37d0a86d09","tid":1970181,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8930b13e0b931e5eabe90dda057c2854f604d053","tid":1970181,"uid":74278,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:10:10.000Z","msg":"你會唔會放條片出黎先比較好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:13:22.000Z","msg":"我傻左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2312982ce3e1402f2317ab9a8f7d87338f52d1ac","tid":1970181,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7e19bf9c0041ec59f0a0a3545a34259cb558fcf","tid":1970181,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:09:09.000Z","msg":"冇link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:45:20.000Z","msg":"慣咗post相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔記得咗件事"},{"pid":"f1db43d862d86e8c5823c73e1a1e5dfd261564f5","tid":1970181,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:49:36.000Z","msg":"Kiki &amp; May - 隨意吃樂部<br />\n9 小時前<br />\nsupport"},{"pid":"8eb8ea6a83d544f581dbfe8dc5d68de1fca26a6b","tid":1970181,"uid":10984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T04:04:41.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e624b344d8890f27f9d70589eb44b8b31bf9f94","tid":1970181,"uid":225818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T04:07:53.000Z","msg":"已訂閱<img src=\"/assets/